[OVERLAY] VimFu — The Vim Grammar
[SAY] Vim is a language. Every command is a verb plus a noun. Operator plus text object.
[SAY] You already know the verbs. D deletes. C changes. Y yanks. Greater-than indents.
[SAY] And you know the nouns. I W, a word. I quote, a string. I paren, a block.
[SAY] C I quote. Change the string.
